options.content:
### Total Value Locked
total value locked across yearn products

panels.description: This counts all tvl on both eth and fantom chains and subtracts for delegated deposited funds in vaults.

targets.expr: (sum(yearn{network="ETH", param="tvl"}) or vector(0)) + (avg(yearn{network="ETH", param="vecrv balance"}) * avg(yearn{network="ETH", param="crv price"}) or vector(0)) + (sum(yearn_vault{network="ETH", param="tvl"}) or vector(0)) + (sum(iearn{network="ETH", param="tvl"}) or vector(0)) + (sum(ironbank{network="ETH", param="tvl"}) or vector(0)) - (sum((yearn_strategy{network="ETH", param="delegatedAssets", experimental="false"} / 1000000000000000000 > 0) * on(vault, version) group_left yearn_vault{network="ETH", param="token price", experimental="false"}) or vector(0)) + (sum(ironbank{network="FTM", param="tvl"}) or vector(0)) + (sum(yearn_vault{network="FTM", param="tvl"}) or vector(0))

panels.title: total

targets.expr: sum(delta(yearn{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1d])) + sum(delta(ironbank{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1d])) + sum(delta(yearn_vault{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1d])) + sum(delta(iearn{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1d])) + sum(delta(yearn_vault{param="tvl", network="FTM"}[1d])) + sum(delta(ironbank{param="tvl", network="FTM"}[1d]))

sum(delta(yearn{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1w])) + sum(delta(ironbank{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1w])) + sum(delta(yearn_vault{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1w])) + sum(delta(iearn{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1w])) + sum(delta(yearn_vault{param="tvl", network="FTM"}[1w])) + sum(delta(ironbank{param="tvl", network="FTM"}[1w]))

(sum(yearn{network="ETH", param="tvl"}) or vector(0)) + (avg(yearn{network="ETH", param="vecrv balance"}) * avg(yearn{network="ETH", param="crv price"}) or vector(0)) + (sum(yearn_vault{network="ETH", param="tvl"}) or vector(0)) + (sum(iearn{network="ETH", param="tvl"}) or vector(0)) + (sum(ironbank{network="ETH", param="tvl"}) or vector(0)) - (sum((yearn_strategy{network="ETH", param="delegatedAssets", experimental="false"} / 1000000000000000000 > 0) * on(vault, version) group_left yearn_vault{network="ETH", param="token price", experimental="false"}) or vector(0))

sum(delta(yearn{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1w])) + sum(delta(ironbank{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1w])) + sum(delta(yearn_vault{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1w])) + sum(delta(iearn{param="tvl", network="ETH"}[1w]))
(sum(ironbank{network="FTM", param="tvl"}) or vector(0)) + (sum(yearn_vault{network="FTM", param="tvl"}) or vector(0))

sum(yearn_vault{param="tvl", network="ETH"}) - (sum((yearn_strategy{param="delegatedAssets", experimental="false", network="ETH"} / 1000000000000000000 > 0) * on(vault, version) group_left yearn_vault{param="token price", experimental="false", network="ETH"}) or vector(0))

sum(yearn_vault{param="tvl", network="FTM"}) - (sum((yearn_strategy{param="delegatedAssets", experimental="false", network="FTM"} / 1000000000000000000 > 0) * on(vault, version) group_left yearn_vault{param="token price", experimental="false", network="FTM"}) or vector(0))
